The product is a Next.js dashboard for Meta Ads analysis. It connects to Meta, lets the user pick an account, campaign scope, date range, KPI pack, and comparison mode, then turns the raw pull into KPI cards, charts, health checks, Verdicts, AI insight briefs, and PDF reports. This snapshot comes from commit 5f84240, feat(auth): add Facebook OAuth login, in tgen16mgc/redagencyads.
